('fb02c000-0000-0000-0000-000000000009','LAS (LiDAR format)','The binary public interchange format for 3D LiDAR point-cloud data. Preferred over ASCII for size/speed; DEM and TIFF are different formats.','Binary LiDAR interchange format.',NULL,NULL,NULL,ARRAY['las','lidar','point cloud']::text[],ARRAY['fs-flashcards','fs-thin-topics','fs-m8']::text[],'fs:f5000008-0000-0000-0000-000000000008','beginner',true,'approved'),
('fb02c000-0000-0000-0000-00000000000a','NSSDA Multipliers','National Standard for Spatial Data Accuracy at 95% confidence: RMSE × 1.7308 for horizontal accuracy, RMSE × 1.9600 for vertical accuracy.','1.7308 horizontal, 1.9600 vertical.',NULL,NULL,NULL,ARRAY['nssda','accuracy','rmse']::text[],ARRAY['fs-flashcards','fs-thin-topics','fs-m8']::text[],'fs:f5000008-0000-0000-0000-000000000008','intermediate',true,'approved'),
('fb02c000-0000-0000-0000-00000000000b','FEMA Elevation Certificate','An NFIP administrative form documenting a structure''s elevation relative to the base flood elevation; used to rate flood insurance and support LOMA/LOMR requests.','Rates flood insurance (NFIP).',NULL,NULL,NULL,ARRAY['elevation certificate','fema','nfip','flood']::text[],ARRAY['fs-flashcards','fs-thin-topics','fs-m8']::text[],'fs:f5000008-0000-0000-0000-000000000008','beginner',true,'approved'),
('fb02c000-0000-0000-0000-00000000000c','Relief Displacement','On a vertical aerial photo, the radial shift of a tall object''s image away from the principal point; it increases with the object''s height and its radial distance.','Radial shift of tall objects.',NULL,NULL,NULL,ARRAY['relief displacement','photogrammetry']::text[],ARRAY['fs-flashcards','fs-thin-topics','fs-m8']::text[],'fs:f5000008-0000-0000-0000-000000000008','advanced',true,'approved'),
('fb02c000-0000-0000-0000-00000000000d','Raster vs Vector','Raster models the world as a grid of cells (pixels) — good for continuous surfaces/imagery. Vector models discrete features as points, lines, and polygons.','Grid of cells vs points/lines/polygons.',NULL,NULL,NULL,ARRAY['raster','vector','gis']::text[],ARRAY['fs-flashcards','fs-thin-topics','fs-m8']::text[],'fs:f5000008-0000-0000-0000-000000000008','beginner',true,'approved'),
